<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's long been known for her chic fashion sense.</p>

<p>And Kelly Brook was proudly displaying her famous curves in a frilled cream blouse as she arrived at Global Studios to present her show on Heart Radio on Monday.</p>

