<p>Lovely: The model teamed the classy top with boot-cut jeans and boots as she headed into the studio in London to present the mid-afternoon show</p>

<p>It comes after Kelly recently revealed that school bullies used to call her 'Smelly Parsnips' when she was younger. </p>

