<p>Lovely: Kelly completed her stylish ensemble with black sunglasses and chain-strapped sunglasses as she headed into the radio studio</p>

<p>In July, Kelly claimed that sex gets better with age and said her longterm love, 35, Jeremy is a big fan of her curves.</p>

<p>Speaking on Vicky Pattison's The Secret To... podcast, she said: 'My boyfriend is 35 and he is Italian, so, you know, he likes a nice large curvy woman so that's always a good thing! I think your sex life gets better as you get older!</p>

